        <name>finalize</name>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Function to finalize SHA1 checksum calculation. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para>Initially the hash will be cleared with call of funtion memset. Afterwards the SHA1 hash checksum will be finalized by calling function mbedtls_sha1_finish and the context variable sha1_ctx will be released by call of function mbedtls_sha1_free, both provided by mbedtls crypto library. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
