    <briefdescription>
<para><ref refid="class_hash" kindref="compound">Hash</ref> class to calculate SHA1 or SHA256 checksum implemented according to C++ singleton design pattern. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para>The <ref refid="class_hash" kindref="compound">Hash</ref> class provides methods to init, updata and finalize a SHA1 or SHA256 hash checksum. Furthermore getter functions to retrieve calculated hash checksum and their length and a method to print out the checksum as string in a terminal window. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
